name: DEPARTMENT OF HUMAN KINETICS AND HEALTH EDUCATION

name: DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH POLICY AND MANAGEMENT

name: DEPARTMENT OF RELIGIOUS STUDIES

name: DEPARTMENT OF MATHEMATICS

name: DEPARTMENT OF COMPUTER SCIENCE

name: DEPARTMENT OF SOCIOLOGY

name: DEPARTMENT OF PHYSIOLOGY

name: DEPARTMENT OF THEATRE ARTS

name: DEPARTMENT OF ANIMAL SCIENCE

name: DEPARTMENT OF MUSIC

name: DEPARTMENT OF GEOGRAPHY

name: DEPARTMENT OF HUMAN NUTRITION

name: DEPARTMENT OF ECONOMICS

name: INSTITUTE OF ADVANCED MEDICAL RESEARCH AND TRAINING

name: DEPARTMENT OF PSYCHOLOGY
description: Studies human behavior, mental processes, and their relationship to brain functions and social environments.
